the best guy with the ball.

00:04:19.700 --> 00:04:23.630
So yeah, I'm rarely a practicing
scientist now,

00:04:23.630 --> 00:04:27.520
although I still review papers
for the AAAI Conference on

00:04:27.520 --> 00:04:28.160
computer games.

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:29.650
TODD KERPELMAN: Wow.

