00:29:29.590 --> 00:29:36.280
But if there is a, this is the
Steam Box game pad that--

00:29:36.280 --> 00:29:40.100
COLT MCANLIS: We need to
go back to power glove.

00:29:40.100 --> 00:29:42.110
Make it happen, Nintendo.

00:29:42.110 --> 00:29:44.080
JOHN MCCUTCHAN: Bring it back.

00:29:44.080 --> 00:29:45.640
WOLFF DOBSON: We gave
you the Wii.

00:29:45.640 --> 00:29:46.480
What do you want?

00:29:46.480 --> 00:29:49.430
COLT MCANLIS: It's not
in glove form.

00:29:49.430 --> 00:29:51.250
So here's my question
for everybody.

00:29:51.250 --> 00:29:52.660
What's driving this?

