It's been probably, in my
personal opinion, keeping

00:29:59.300 --> 00:30:01.850
gaming on desktops alive.

00:30:01.850 --> 00:30:03.540
TODD KERPELMAN: I think they've
done a huge service to

00:30:03.540 --> 00:30:04.430
the PC gaming industry.

00:30:04.430 --> 00:30:04.870
COLT MCANLIS: Absolutely.

00:30:04.870 --> 00:30:06.576
When we saw consoles
taking over, we

00:30:06.576 --> 00:30:07.490
saw a big trend there.

00:30:07.490 --> 00:30:11.230
Even the switch to mobile and
web now, I think it's safe to

00:30:11.230 --> 00:30:13.620
