treadmill, which was every

00:32:40.310 --> 00:32:43.660
year a new game came that
required a new GPU and a new

00:32:43.660 --> 00:32:44.970
faster CPU.

00:32:44.970 --> 00:32:46.850
TODD KERPELMAN: It made you
feel awesome when you went

00:32:46.850 --> 00:32:49.770
down to the store and you're
